{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"建立或觸發事件","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/Guide/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>本文介紹如何建立和觸發事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"建立自定義事件","title":"建立自定義事件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>事件可以用&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> constructor 建立，如下所示：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 監聽事件</span>\nelem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 觸發事件</span>\nelem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>除了 Internet Explorer 以外，大多數的瀏覽器都支持這個 constructor&nbsp;。若要能夠支援 Internet Explore 的更詳細的方法，可以參考段落《<a href=\"#早期的做法\" title=\"早期的作法\">早期的做法</a>》。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"增加自定義的資料－－customevent()","title":"增加自定義的資料－－CustomEvent()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>要在事件的 object 追加其他資料，能使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a> 介面。它有 <u><strong>detail</strong></u>&nbsp;屬性，可以用來傳送自訂資料。<br>\n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">舉例來說，可以以下面方式建立事件：</span></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CustomEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string-property property\">'detail'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dataset<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>time <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>它可以讓你傳送自訂資料到事件的監聽器：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">eventHandler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The time is: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>detail<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"早期的做法","title":"早期的做法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>早期建立事件的方式參考了 Java 的&nbsp;API&nbsp;。下為一個早期作法的例子：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 建立事件</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 設定事件名稱為 “build” 。</span>\nevent<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 監聽事件</span>\nelem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// e.target matches elem</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 事件對象可以是任一 HTML 元素或是 EventTarget 。</span>\nelem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"觸發自定義事件","title":"觸發自定義事件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的例子演示了一個複選框藉由 DOM 的 methods 模擬一次點擊（換言之，讓程式執行一次「點擊事件」。）。 <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://developer.mozilla.org/samples/domref/dispatchEvent.html\" rel=\" noopener\">觀看實例</a>。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">simulateClick</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MouseEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'view'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'bubbles'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'cancelable'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> cb <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'checkbox'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canceled <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>cb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>canceled<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// A handler called preventDefault.</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canceled\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// None of the handlers called preventDefault.</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"not canceled\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"瀏覽器的支援度","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sect1","title":"&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Feature</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Chrome</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Edge</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Opera</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Event()</code>&nbsp;constructor</td>\n   <td>15</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td>11.60</td>\n   <td>6</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Feature</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Android</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">IE Mobile</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>6</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>","titleAsText":" "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸閱讀","title":"延伸閱讀","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document/createEvent\"><code>document.createEvent()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/initEvent\"><code>Event.initEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"建立自定義事件","id":"建立自定義事件"},{"text":"觸發自定義事件","id":"觸發自定義事件"},{"text":"瀏覽器的支援度","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"&nbsp;","id":"sect1"},{"text":"延伸閱讀","id":"延伸閱讀"}],"summary":"本文介紹如何建立和觸發事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/web/guide/events/creating_and_triggering_events","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/web/guide/events/creating_and_triggering_events/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/Guide/Events","title":"Event developer guide"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/Guide/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events","title":"建立或觸發事件"}],"pageTitle":"建立或觸發事件 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}